22#ifndef BUDBG_H
23#define BUDBG_H
24
25/* Routine used to read generic debugging information. */
26
27extern void *read_debugging_info (bfd *, asymbol **, long, bfd_boolean);
28
29/* Routine used to print generic debugging information. */
30
31extern bfd_boolean print_debugging_info
32 (FILE *, void *, bfd *, asymbol **,
33 char * (*) (struct bfd *, const char *, int), bfd_boolean);
34
35/* Routines used to read and write stabs information. */
36
37extern void *start_stab (void *, bfd *, bfd_boolean, asymbol **, long);
38
39extern bfd_boolean finish_stab (void *, void *);
40
41extern bfd_boolean parse_stab
42 (void *, void *, int, int, bfd_vma, const char *);
43
44extern bfd_boolean write_stabs_in_sections_debugging_info
45 (bfd *, void *, bfd_byte **, bfd_size_type *, bfd_byte **, bfd_size_type *);
46
47/* Routine used to read COFF debugging information. */
48
49extern bfd_boolean parse_coff (bfd *, asymbol **, long, void *);
50
51#endif
